snippet.title: Version 4.8 "Summertide Scales and Tales" Trailer | Genshin Impact #Trailer #GenshinImpact
snippet.description:
Here are some summer essentials:
A refreshing fragrance to soothe restless emotions in the sweltering sun,
A storybook you've never read to brighten a lackadaisical holiday,
And just a hint of looming peril to satisfy curious minds eager for secrets.

VA:
Tighnari — Zachary Gordon
Paimon — Corina Boettger
Emilie — Amber Aviles
Kirara — Julia Gu
Nilou — Dani Chambers
Navia — Brenna Larsen
Wanderer — Patrick Pedraza
